    <briefdescription>
<para>\par \b Purpose\/ \:  Produce a flat linear document structure where every line is a direct child of the root node — the fallback/simplest representation. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class is used to form a simple basic document structure representation as a list of document lines. The result contains the empty root node with the consecutive list of all document lines as its children. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
